Cam-Scom

Cam::Scom provides asynchronous reading and writing
on multiple filehandles from a single process and thread.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

    perldoc Cam::Scom

